### Profile Setup Page — Multi-Step Wizard

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///j:/PaceUp/app/dashboard/profile/setup/page.tsx)

Complete rewrite into a multi-step wizard with:

**Step 1 — Personal Overview** (Tell us about yourself)
- Professional headline (text input)
- Short bio / professional summary (textarea, 280 char max)
- Location (text input with autocomplete feel)
- LinkedIn URL (optional)
- GitHub URL (optional)
- Portfolio URL (optional)

**Step 2 — Technical Arsenal** (What can you build with?)
- Programming languages — multi-select grid, PLUS a proficiency slider per selected language (Beginner → Intermediate → Advanced → Expert) and years of experience
- Frameworks & libraries — searchable tag input (React, Next.js, Express, Django, Flask, Spring Boot, Flutter, etc.)
- Tools — multi-select grid (Git, Docker, Kubernetes, Figma, Jira, Notion, VS Code, etc.)
- Databases — multi-select (PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, Redis, Firebase, Supabase, etc.)
